p3dx_gazebo

The p3dx_gazebo package. This is a first working version.

  • Homepage: http://wiki.ros.org/p3dx_gazebo

This package contains launch files and Gazebo worlds for simulating a Pioneer P3-DX differential mobile base. At the time the only worlds working with the provided launch files are p3dx.word and map1_wo_robot.world .
